org.sql: SELECT time_entries.* FROM time_entries INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = time_entries.project_id WHERE time_entries.created_on BETWEEN '2022-01-14' AND '2022-02-14' AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13))
